Privacy Policy
User Privacy Policy Agreement
Thank you for using our App Poster software (hereinafter referred to as "Software"). In order to protect your personal privacy rights, we will explain how we handle and protect your personal information. Please carefully read this Privacy Policy Agreement (hereinafter referred to as "Agreement") before using this software.
1. Information Collection
We solemnly promise that this software will not collect, store or transmit any information related to your personal identity. We are committed to protecting your personal privacy and complying with relevant laws and regulations of the People's Republic of China.
2. Information Usage
As this software does not collect user information, we will not use your personal information for any purpose, including but not limited to advertising placement, user analysis or other commercial purposes.
3. Information Disclosure
Based on the principle of not collecting user information, we will not disclose your personal information to any third party, including government departments, enterprises or individuals.
4. Information Security
We will take reasonable technical and managerial measures to ensure your personal information security. We will take necessary measures to prevent unauthorized access, use, disclosure, modification or damage to your personal information.
5. Minors' Privacy Protection
This software is not open to minors under the age of 18. We recommend that minors use this software under the guidance of a guardian, and minors should not provide any personal information to us.
6. Legal Applicability and Dispute Resolution
This Agreement shall be governed by the laws of the People's Republic of China. If any dispute arises due to this Agreement, both parties shall negotiate and resolve it amicably. If the negotiation fails, either party has the right to submit the dispute to the people's court with jurisdiction for resolution in the place where the agreement is signed.
7. Privacy Policy Updates and Notification
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. We will publish the updated Privacy Policy through the Software and notify you in advance a reasonable time before the update takes effect. Your continued use of this software indicates that you accept the updated Privacy Policy.
If you have any questions or comments about this Privacy Policy, please contact us. We will do our best to provide necessary support and answers.
